  <entry>
    <title>【折腾记录】iPad代码流：在云服务器上远程使用Neovim编辑器</title>
    <link href="http://shinotak.com/2022/04/08/Records/Neovim/"/>
    <id>http://shinotak.com/2022/04/08/Records/Neovim/</id>
    <published>2022-04-08T06:32:03.000Z</published>
    <updated>2022-07-27T00:36:11.183Z</updated>
    
    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<blockquote><p>前言：为了折腾这玩意我删了三次库…后来才发现腾讯云可以设置服务器快照…</p></blockquote><h2 id="一、iPad端：Termius-App"><a href="#一、iPad端：Termius-App" class="headerlink" title="一、iPad端：Termius App"></a>一、iPad端：Termius App</h2><h2 id="二、服务器：腾讯云服务器（CentOS-7）"><a href="#二、服务器：腾讯云服务器（CentOS-7）" class="headerlink" title="二、服务器：腾讯云服务器（CentOS 7）"></a>二、服务器：腾讯云服务器（CentOS 7）</h2><h3 id="1、安装-Tmux：终端复用器"><a href="#1、安装-Tmux：终端复用器" class="headerlink" title="1、安装 Tmux：终端复用器"></a>1、安装 Tmux：终端复用器</h3><blockquote><p>安装前注意参考<a href="https://github.com/tmux/tmux/wiki/Installing">官方wiki文档</a></p></blockquote><p>安装方法有如下三种：</p><ul><li>直接使用 <code>yum install tmux</code> 安装官方库提供的版本：在 CentOS 中，该版本较旧，无法使用 oh-my-tmux 进行界面美化。</li><li>下载源文件，利用官方提供的脚本进行安装：具体步骤参考官方wiki即可。</li><li>安装第三方库，从第三方库中获取 RPM 包并安装：在文档中，提及了使用 Galaxy4 第三方库的具体方法。</li></ul><blockquote><p>具体细节可参考Galaxy4库的<a href="https://anni.galaxy4.net/?page_id=39">网站说明</a></p></blockquote><p>虽然 Galaxy4 库中 Tmux 的版本并非最新版，但已满足需求，为求安装简便，选择使用第三种方法：</p><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="comment"># 安装 galaxy4</span></span><br><span class="line">yum install http://galaxy4.net/repo/galaxy4-release-7-current.noarch.rpm</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment"># 利用 yum 安装 tmux</span></span><br><span class="line">yum install tmux</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment"># 检验安装是否成功</span></span><br><span class="line">tmux -v</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h3 id="2、-配置-Tmux："><a href="#2、-配置-Tmux：" class="headerlink" title="2、 配置 Tmux："></a>2、 配置 Tmux：</h3><p>Tmux 允许高度定制，可以定制自己的键位习惯、美化风格等。</p><p>此处直接使用较受欢迎、较为通用的配置：<a href="https://github.com/gpakosz/.tmux">oh-my-tmux</a>。</p><blockquote><p>oh-my-tmux 安装条件：</p><ul><li>tmux <strong><code>&gt;= 2.3</code></strong> (soon) running inside Linux, Mac, OpenBSD, Cygwin or WSL<code>&gt;= 2.4</code></li><li>awk, perl and sed</li><li>outside of tmux, must be set to <code>$TERM``xterm-256color</code></li></ul></blockquote><h4 id="（1）配置方法："><a href="#（1）配置方法：" class="headerlink" title="（1）配置方法："></a>（1）配置方法：</h4><p>默认配置步骤如下：</p><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="comment"># 进入用户主目录</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="built_in">cd</span></span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment"># 在用户主目录下克隆仓库</span></span><br><span class="line">git <span class="built_in">clone</span> https://github.com/gpakosz/.tmux.git</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment"># 建立到配置文件的软连接</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="built_in">ln</span> -s -f .tmux/.tmux.conf</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment"># 复制.tmux.conf.local到当前目录下，以便用户自定义使用</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="built_in">cp</span> .tmux/.tmux.conf.local .</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>自定义配置步骤如下：</p><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="comment"># 新建存储 oh-my-tmux 配置的文件夹</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="built_in">mkdir</span> /path/to/oh-my-tmux</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment"># 将文件 clone 至已新建好的文件夹内</span></span><br><span class="line">git <span class="built_in">clone</span> https://github.com/gpakosz/.tmux.git /path/to/oh-my-tmux</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment"># 建立 oh-my-tmux 的配置文件软连接以便在主目录下直接访问</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="built_in">ln</span> -s -f /path/to/oh-my-tmux/.tmux.conf ~/.tmux.conf</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment"># 复制 .tmux.conf.local 文件，以便于用户自定义使用</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="built_in">cp</span> /path/to/oh-my-tmux/.tmux.conf.local ~/.tmux.conf.local</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h4 id="（2）启用样式："><a href="#（2）启用样式：" class="headerlink" title="（2）启用样式："></a>（2）启用样式：</h4><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="comment"># 使用 vim 编辑 .bashrc 文件</span></span><br><span class="line">vim ~/.bashrc</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment"># 在 .bashrc 中添加环境变量，对于vim使用者设置 $EDITOR 环境变量为 vim 或 nvim</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="built_in">export</span> EDITOR=vim</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment"># 重新加载该文件进行配置刷新</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="built_in">source</span> ~/.bashrc</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h4 id="（3）解决-iPad-SSH-客户端颜色显示偏差："><a href="#（3）解决-iPad-SSH-客户端颜色显示偏差：" class="headerlink" title="（3）解决 iPad SSH 客户端颜色显示偏差："></a>（3）解决 iPad SSH 客户端颜色显示偏差：</h4><blockquote><p>在一些 SSH 客户端使用 Tmux 可能无法显示真彩色，如 iPad 上的 Termius。</p><p>出现颜色偏差的原因：在进入 Tmux 后使用 echo $TERM，显示screen-256color；而在不使用 Tmux 时输入该命令显示 xterm-256color。</p></blockquote><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="comment"># 修改 .tmux.conf 配置文件</span></span><br><span class="line">vim ~/.tmux.conf</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment"># 添加如下配置让 Tmux 重载终端，即可使其正确识别</span></span><br><span class="line">set-option -sa terminal-overrides <span class="string">&#x27;,xterm-256color:RGB&#x27;</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h3 id="3、-安装Neovim：基于Vim进行升级的代码编辑器"><a href="#3、-安装Neovim：基于Vim进行升级的代码编辑器" class="headerlink" title="3、 安装Neovim：基于Vim进行升级的代码编辑器"></a>3、 安装Neovim：基于Vim进行升级的代码编辑器</h3><blockquote><p>安装前注意参考<a href="https://github.com/neovim/neovim/wiki/Installing-Neovim">官方wiki文档</a></p></blockquote><p>安装方法主要有如下两种：</p><ul><li>通过第三方库 epel 使用 yum 包管理命令安装：版本较旧。</li></ul><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">yum install -y https://dl.fedoraproject.org/pub/epel/epel-release-latest-7.noarch.rpm</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">yum install -y neovim python3-neovim</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><ul><li>通过编译源码进行安装：可安装最新版本，推荐。</li></ul><p>此处使用第二种方法进行安装，但在该方法的基础上有更加便捷的衍生方法。</p><blockquote><p>对于该方法，安装前注意参考<a href="https://github.com/neovim/neovim/wiki/Building-Neovim">官方wiki文档中的说明</a></p></blockquote><h4 id="（1）-解决相关依赖："><a href="#（1）-解决相关依赖：" class="headerlink" title="（1） 解决相关依赖："></a>（1） 解决相关依赖：</h4><blockquote><p>编译环境要求：</p><p>Clang or GCC version 4.4+</p><p>CMake version 3.10+, built with TLS&#x2F;SSL support</p></blockquote><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="comment"># 官方wiki中提供的“一站式”安装依赖文件的命令</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment"># 使用该方法安装的 cmake 版本较低，为 2.x</span></span><br><span class="line">yum -y install ninja-build libtool autoconf automake cmake gcc gcc-c++ make pkgconfig unzip patch gettext curl</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment"># 此处建议使用如下命令，与上一条命令相比只更换了 cmake 的版本，为 3.x</span></span><br><span class="line">yum -y install ninja-build libtool autoconf automake cmake3 gcc gcc-c++ make pkgconfig unzip patch gettext curl</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><blockquote><p>注：</p><p>对于使用第一条命令，需要升级 cmake，升级方法如下：</p><ul><li>源码安装方法：<a href="https://www.cnblogs.com/huizhipeng/p/12731576.html">Centos7 cmake 版本升级（由 v2.8.12.2 升级至 v3.16.6）</a></li></ul><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="comment"># 注意 wget 下载的版本</span></span><br><span class="line">wget https://cmake.org/files/v3.23/cmake-3.23.0.tar.gz</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><ul><li>使用第三方库配合 yum 安装：</li></ul><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="comment"># 检查所有关联库中 cmake 的包信息</span></span><br><span class="line">yum list CMake3</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment"># 如果此前已经安装了第三方库 epel ，则会显示该库中 cmake 的较新版本信息</span></span><br><span class="line">yum install cmake3</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></blockquote><h4 id="（2）源码下载："><a href="#（2）源码下载：" class="headerlink" title="（2）源码下载："></a>（2）源码下载：</h4><p>法一：neovim 项目文件较大，下载速度较慢</p><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="comment"># 新建文件夹</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="built_in">mkdir</span> /opt/Neovim</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment"># 进入文件夹内</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="built_in">cd</span> /opt/Neovim</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment"># 使用 clone 获取项目</span></span><br><span class="line">git <span class="built_in">clone</span> https://github.com/neovim/neovim.git</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment"># 选择稳定版进行构建</span></span><br><span class="line">git checkout stable</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>法二：</p><p>在 Github 项目的 [Releases 界面](<a href="https://github.com/neovim/neovim/releases">Releases · neovim&#x2F;neovim · GitHub</a>)，下载最新稳定版的源码包。</p><p>之后使用 Xftp 等类似软件，直接将本地文件传入服务器中的目标文件夹。</p><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="comment"># 对源码包进行解压缩</span></span><br><span class="line">tar -zxvf neovim-xxx.tar.gz</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h4 id="（3）编译安装"><a href="#（3）编译安装" class="headerlink" title="（3）编译安装"></a>（3）编译安装</h4><p>默认路径安装方法（&#x2F;usr&#x2F;local）：</p><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="comment"># 进入下载好或解压好的源码文件夹</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="built_in">cd</span> /opt/Neovim/neovim</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment"># 设置构建类型为发行版并编译，此时会下载一系列编译需要用到的文件</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment"># 由于是从 Github 中下载，会经常存在连接超时而下载失败的问题</span></span><br><span class="line">make CMAKE_BUILD_TYPE=Release</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment"># 安装</span></span><br><span class="line">make install</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>自定义路径安装方法：</p><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br><span class="line">12</span><br><span class="line">13</span><br><span class="line">14</span><br><span class="line">15</span><br><span class="line">16</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="comment"># 进入下载好或解压好的源码文件夹</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="built_in">cd</span> /opt/Neovim/neovim</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment"># 设置构建类型为发行版</span></span><br><span class="line">make CMAKE_BUILD_TYPE=Release</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment"># 设置自定义安装目录</span></span><br><span class="line">make CMAKE_INSTALL_PREFIX=<span class="variable">$HOME</span>/neovim</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment"># 安装</span></span><br><span class="line">make install</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment"># 配置环境变量</span></span><br><span class="line">vim ~/.bashrc</span><br><span class="line"><span class="built_in">export</span> PATH=<span class="string">&quot;<span class="variable">$HOME</span>/neovim/bin:<span class="variable">$PATH</span>&quot;</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="built_in">source</span> ~/.bashrc</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>检验是否安装成功：</p><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">nvim -version</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><blockquote><p>注：</p><p>由于编译时需要从 Github 获取编译所需文件，故容易连接超时而报错</p><p>可以采用如下方法：</p><p>例如，提示 busted-2.0.0.tar.gz 下载失败，可以按照提示的 Github 链接手动下载，并通过 Xftp 等软件传送到 .&#x2F;neovim&#x2F;.deps&#x2F;build&#x2F;downloads&#x2F; 目录中，并修改权限为777即可</p></blockquote><h3 id="4、-配置-Neovim："><a href="#4、-配置-Neovim：" class="headerlink" title="4、 配置 Neovim："></a>4、 配置 Neovim：</h3><p>Neovim 同样允许高度定制化。而作为入门小白，此处直接参考使用 <a href="https://github.com/LunarVim/LunarVim">LunarVim</a> 的配置方案。</p><blockquote><p>配置方法请参照 <a href="https://www.lunarvim.org/">LunarVim 文档</a>中的 Installation 部分。</p></blockquote><br><h2 id="未完待续"><a href="#未完待续" class="headerlink" title="未完待续"></a>未完待续</h2><br><h2 id="参考链接："><a href="#参考链接：" class="headerlink" title="参考链接："></a>参考链接：</h2><ol><li><a href="https://zhuanlan.zhihu.com/p/373100540]">iPad上的最强开发环境——1，iPad上学习编程的首选方式 - 知乎 (zhihu.com)</a></li><li><a href="https://zhuanlan.zhihu.com/p/382092667">我的现代化Neovim配置 - 知乎 (zhihu.com)</a></li></ol>]]></content>
    
    
