  <entry>
    <title>【贴士】Use Nodejs on MacOS</title>
    <link href="http://shinotak.com/2022/01/30/Tips/UseNodejsOnMac/"/>
    <id>http://shinotak.com/2022/01/30/Tips/UseNodejsOnMac/</id>
    <published>2022-01-29T16:02:10.000Z</published>
    <updated>2022-07-27T01:58:50.740Z</updated>
    
    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<p>直接使用官网提供的pkg进行安装虽然简单快捷，但是删除卸载时需要深入文件夹进行删除操作，在不清楚相关目录结构的情况下贸然使用rm -rf是有极大风险的。所以在这里推荐使用 Mac OS 下的包管理工具 brew 来进行安装以及管理。</p><hr><h2 id="对于使用pkg安装的卸载"><a href="#对于使用pkg安装的卸载" class="headerlink" title="对于使用pkg安装的卸载"></a>对于使用pkg安装的卸载</h2><ol><li>打开终端，输入如下命令：</li></ol><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="comment"># sudo调用root权限，对Node相关目录使用rm -rf指令递归删除所有文件夹与目录。</span></span><br><span class="line">sudo <span class="built_in">rm</span> -rf /usr/local/&#123;bin/&#123;node,npm&#125;,lib/node_modules/npm,lib/node,share/man/*/node.*&#125;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><ol start="2"><li>通过下面一系列指令，清理遗留文件：</li></ol><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">sudo <span class="built_in">rm</span> /usr/local/bin/npm</span><br><span class="line">sudo <span class="built_in">rm</span> /usr/local/share/man/man1/node.1</span><br><span class="line">sudo <span class="built_in">rm</span> /usr/local/lib/dtrace/node.d</span><br><span class="line">sudo <span class="built_in">rm</span> -rf ~/.npm</span><br><span class="line">sudo <span class="built_in">rm</span> -rf ~/.node-gyp</span><br><span class="line">sudo <span class="built_in">rm</span> /opt/local/bin/node</span><br><span class="line">sudo <span class="built_in">rm</span> /opt/local/include/node</span><br><span class="line">sudo <span class="built_in">rm</span> -rf /opt/local/lib/node_modules</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><hr><h2 id="前置准备：安装brew"><a href="#前置准备：安装brew" class="headerlink" title="前置准备：安装brew"></a>前置准备：安装brew</h2><p>如果设备中没有安装brew，请打开终端输入如下命令：</p><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">/bin/bash -c <span class="string">&quot;<span class="subst">$(curl -fsSL https://raw.githubusercontent.com/Homebrew/install/HEAD/install.sh)</span>&quot;</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>如果安装失败，可以尝试使用如下命令：</p><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">/usr/bin/ruby -e <span class="string">&quot;<span class="subst">$(curl -fsSL https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/ineo6/homebrew-install/install)</span>&quot;</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><blockquote><p>注：官方提供的安装命令是从github仓库获取，而由于在国内访问github的情况并不理想，故此处使用了jsDelivr（提供免费npm、github加速的CDN公共服务，可加速访问在github上托管的项目或图片资源，其在国内拥有备案以及数个国内加速节点），使用格式为 <a href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/user/repo@version/file">https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/user/repo@version/file</a> ，即上述命令中网址连接的前半部分。</p></blockquote><p>如果出现其他问题，请善用搜索引擎。</p><hr><h2 id="使用brew安装"><a href="#使用brew安装" class="headerlink" title="使用brew安装"></a>使用brew安装</h2><ol><li>打开终端，输入如下命令：</li></ol><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">brew install node</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>该指令默认安装node的最新版本。如需安装其他版本，可以进行如下操作：</p><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="comment"># 查找node所有可用软件包</span></span><br><span class="line">brew search node</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment"># 选择需要安装的版本（如：node@16）</span></span><br><span class="line">brew install node@16</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><ol start="2"><li>安装完成后，终端输入如下指令检验安装：</li></ol><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">node -v</span><br><span class="line">npm -v</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>一般情况下进行到此步便安装成功，即输入命令后返回已安装版本号。</p><hr><h2 id="排错：command-not-found"><a href="#排错：command-not-found" class="headerlink" title="排错：command not found"></a>排错：command not found</h2><h3 id="问题分析："><a href="#问题分析：" class="headerlink" title="问题分析："></a>问题分析：</h3><p>笔者在卸载重装后，检验安装时会报错：command not found。经过查阅资料得知，brew在安装软件包时会自动执行brew link命令，用以在&#x2F;usr&#x2F;local&#x2F;bin目录下创建链接文件，并将该文件与已下载软件包（存放在&#x2F;usr&#x2F;local&#x2F;Cellar目录下）中的相关可执行文件进行软链接。而当软链接不存在或出现错误时，便无法直接使用（或者说在任意目录位置使用）node相关指令，此时只有进入到软件包存放可执行文件的目录（一般为&#x2F;bin目录）内才能执行成功。</p><p>以node来举例就是：</p><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br><span class="line">12</span><br><span class="line">13</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="comment"># 暂时获取root权限</span></span><br><span class="line">su -u root</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment"># 进入/usr/local/bin目录</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="built_in">cd</span> /usr/local/bin</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment"># 查看node的连接文件</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="built_in">ls</span> -l | grep node</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment"># 查询结果如下：</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment"># &quot;lrwxr-xr-x&quot;：第一个字母即代表该文件为链接文件（可类比windows中的快捷方式）</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment"># &quot;node -&gt; ../Cellar/...&quot;：&quot;-&gt;&quot;指向的目录地址即为其链接的文件</span></span><br><span class="line">lrwxr-xr-x  1 wangzai  admin     30 Jan 29 22:04 node -&gt; ../Cellar/node/17.4.0/bin/node</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><blockquote><p>通过brew link可以实现多版本的混合使用。</p><p>比如当想使用node@16时，可以通过执行brew unlink node和brew link node@16将软链接切换至16版本。</p></blockquote><h3 id="解决方案："><a href="#解决方案：" class="headerlink" title="解决方案："></a>解决方案：</h3><p>原则上可以依次执行如下命令。</p><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="comment"># 使用管理员权限，将/usr/local目录以及其下子目录和文件的拥有者改为当前用户（即whoami的返回值）</span></span><br><span class="line">sudo <span class="built_in">chown</span> -R $(<span class="built_in">whoami</span>) /usr/local</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment"># 强制重写软链接以建立正确连接</span></span><br><span class="line">brew <span class="built_in">link</span> --overwrite node</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment"># 重新运行软件包安装后步骤（Rerun the post-install steps for formula.）</span></span><br><span class="line">brew postinstall node</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>此时再次输入node -v与npm -v指令检验安装即可。</p><blockquote><p>注：此处笔者只执行了前两条指令，之后检验安装成功。目前不清楚第三步所指的“安装后步骤”是哪些，以及不执行第三步会出现什么问题。之后会再进行补充。</p></blockquote><hr><h2 id="对于使用brew安装的卸载"><a href="#对于使用brew安装的卸载" class="headerlink" title="对于使用brew安装的卸载"></a>对于使用brew安装的卸载</h2><p>运行如下指令即可：</p><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">brew uninstall node</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>如果有多版本，就相应运行：（此处以nod@16为例）</p><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">brew uninstall node@16</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><hr><blockquote><p>参考文章：</p><ol><li><a href="https://brew.sh/index_zh-cn">homebrew官方中文页</a></li><li><a href="https://www.jianshu.com/p/0868379a2444">简书：MacOS 安装 Homebrew 失败的解决方案</a></li><li><a href="https://www.jianshu.com/p/c8473afd7dcb">简书：如何在Mac电脑上完全卸载node.js</a></li><li><a href="https://blog.csdn.net/qq_16845639/article/details/77812279">CSDN：”env: node: No such file or directory”的解决办法</a></li><li><a href="https://stackoverflow.com/questions/33268389/what-does-brew-link-do">StackOverFlow：What does “brew link” do?</a></li><li><a href="https://blog.csdn.net/weixin_33758863/article/details/86229522">CSDN：chown -R命令的使用</a></li><li><a href="https://docs.brew.sh/Manpage#postinstall-installed_formula-">brew官方文档：postinstall命令</a></li></ol></blockquote>]]></content>
    
    
